    "simple_text_T8WWHW": {
      "type": "simple-text",
      "settings": {
        "color_scheme": "scheme-399d772c-5473-4d93-a407-2288d88a4cf1",
        "header": "Simplifying Your Buying Process",
        "heading_font_size": 32,
        "paragraph": "<p>Once you have your design finalized, itâ€™s time to make the purchase. With all of the different types of products and purchasing methods, it can be confusing. Depending upon the item that is being purchased, it can be a quick exchange, a short-term, or even a long-term plan with multiple steps. Here at Theplaygroundstore.com we like to keep things simple because it should be simple!<\/p>",
        "text_font_size": 18,
        "alignment": "left",
        "padding_top": 16,
        "padding_bottom": 32
      }
    },
    "multirow_dhHBNH": {
      "type": "multirow",
      "blocks": {
        "row_gWdafX": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/iphone-quote-view.png",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "1.) Submit Your Quote",
            "text": "<p>This is after you have decided your purchase. Your order will be sent to our representative who will then create a quote based on your selection. <\/p><p>For more efficient service, place note in the comment section if you are interested in surfacing or installation services.<\/p>",
            "button_label": "Shop to Begin Quote",
            "button_link": "\/collections\/"
          }
        },
        "row_kPwVnD": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AdobeStock_387159171.jpg",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "2.) Receive Quote",
            "text": "<p>Once your quote cart has been reviewed, an e-mail will come with a formal quote. <\/p><p>The quote needs to be submitted within a few weeks to ensure the price as shipping fluctuates over time.<\/p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_7DahzV": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AdobeStock_119998472.jpg",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "3.) Choose Payment",
            "text": "<p>There are four different ways to pay:<\/p><ul><li>Pay in full<\/li><li>Pay a percentage<\/li><li>Submit a P.O. <\/li><li>Finance<\/li><\/ul><p><\/p><p>Paying in full is always the simplest for both parties. <\/p><p>When you a elect to pay a percentage, your sales representative will work with you on how to split the payments. One portion is paid upon ordering and the remainder is paid before shipping. <\/p><p>P.O.s are only available for governmental organizations.<\/p><p> For more information about our financing, check out our Financing Guide.<\/p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_iCVTYi": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/man-holding-clipboard.jpg",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "4.) Verify Order",
            "text": "<p>At this point you will want to double check the details of your order. You will verify color choices for the structure or item, confirm your shipping address and date of installation among other details.<\/p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_6LUTDk": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/online-shopping.jpg",
            "caption": "Caption",
            "heading": "5.) Submit Payment",
            "text": "<p>We accept Mastercard and Visa as well as most major credit cards and wire transfer. <\/p><p>A salesperson will confirm colors, addresses and other important information with you after receiving payment.<\/p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
